<bibRefCitation author="Zeity M. &amp; Srinivasa N." box="[730,1000,1802,1826]" pageId="2" pageNumber="269" pagination="529 - 543" refId="ref7509" refString="Zeity M., Srinivasa N. 2019. Updated contribution to the knowledge of Tetranychoidea (Acari: Tetranychidae, Tenuipalpidae) from Syria with reinstatement of genus Nuciforaella Vacante. Syst. Appl. Acarol., 24 (4): 529 - 543. doi: 10.11158 / saa. 24.4.1" type="journal article" year="2019">Zeity and Srinivasa, 2019</bibRefCitation>
